songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Mark Sanchez + Action Bronson]
I'm looking for the, uh—the best rapper in Flushing Queens
Yeah, this is him
Uh, this must be Action?
This is Action
What' up, dude? It's Sanchez
What's going on, Sanchez Sanchize? What's up, my brother? How's everything?
Hahaha. This is Mark Sanchez and you're listening to Action Bronson
songs.title: Mark Sanchez
